"<mousebutton>Vasaku</mousebutton> ja <mousebutton>keskmise</mousebutton> "
"hiirenupu toimimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you click the &LMB; on an item in &konqueror;'s window, it will be "
