#~ msgid ""
#~ "If the toolbars are unlocked, on the left hand end of each bar you can "
#~ "see some handles. By &LMB; clicking on them, you can drag a bar into a "
#~ "new position and even detach it from the window and place it anywhere on "
#~ "your screen."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Kui tööriistaribad on lukustamata, on iga riba vasakus servas mõned "
